                    priority_id,
                    tx_id,
                    block_number,
                    sender,
                    receiver,
                    value,
                    calldata,
                    canonical_tx_hash,
                    created_at

                VALUES
                ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
                ON CONFLICT (tx_id) DO NOTHING
